    <!-- 
      Application Structure Plan: A tabbed SPA interface.
      - Tab 1: Overview (Profile, KPIs, Competencies) - For a quick, high-level summary.
      - Tab 2: Lemongrass (Mondelez, SRAM) - A deep dive into the most recent, relevant work.
      - Tab 3: CENIT (Career Progression) - Shows history, software-led sales foundation, and loyalty.
      - Tab 4: History (Earlier Roles, Education) - Supporting background information.
      This structure allows a user (like a hiring manager) to choose their journey: get the 30-second pitch (Overview) or explore the proof points (Lemongrass/CENIT).
    -->
    <!-- 
      Visualization & Content Choices:
      - Performance KPIs (106%, $8.6M, $25M+): Goal: Inform (key metrics). Method: High-contrast "Stat Card" grid. Interaction: None. Justification: Grabs attention, proves performance immediately.
      - Quota Chart ($8.6M vs $9.1M~): Goal: Compare (Quota vs. Attainment). Method: Bar Chart (Chart.js). Interaction: Tooltip on hover. Justification: Visually reinforces the "106% Attainment" claim.
      - Career Progression (CENIT): Goal: Organize (Show growth). Method: Styled HTML timeline/list. Interaction: None. Justification: Clearly shows progression from AM to Sales Director.
      - Key Accounts (Mondelez/SRAM): Goal: Inform (Project Details). Method: Clickable sub-tabs/sections. Interaction: Click to toggle. Justification: Separates projects for clarity.
    -->
    <!-- 
      CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. 
